{"type":"article","id":17016,"title":"【二次爆发】微博话题#常州金新鼎邦#，巴西归国确诊后儿子跑遍半个城","uid":18252,"topics":[7877,1257,5262],"contents":"<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/82xTqu1.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/82xTqu1.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/82xTqu1.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n一位巴西归国的董事长，托关系+钱搞了居家隔离，但富二代儿子到处乱跑，常州市已经传闻了三四天，儿子和接机的滴滴司机确诊。<br>\n<br>\n巴西儿子去了酒吧、餐馆、便利店、洗车店（据说是他自己的生意，很多门店都去了）、各个小区去谈生意……目前据传常州市隔离了上千人。<br>\n<br>\n但至今官方未予以通报。常州人民刷微博热搜被撤。<br>\n<br>\n如今接触巴西儿子的人已经绿码变红码。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/bkmsOAu.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bkmsOAu.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/bkmsOAu.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/3cA5Bn0.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3cA5Bn0.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/3cA5Bn0.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<b>今日江苏省及常州市依然未官方通报</b><br>\n<br>\n<b>今日起江苏省高三年级与初三年级正式复课</b>","date":"2020-03-31","agreeCount":3,"discussionCount":0}